# Normalize line endings to LF in the repo and in every working copy.
# Without this, core.autocrlf=true gives Windows checkouts CRLF files, which
# Prettier (endOfLine defaults to "lf") flags — making `npm run check` fail
# locally even though CI (which checks out LF) is green. eol=lf overrides
# autocrlf so every platform sees LF and the check passes everywhere.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Don't touch the binary distribution bundle.
*.skill binary
